{"tid":1673392,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞感謝日注意事項 歡迎手足補充","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T05:53:18.000Z","uid":225531,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"57ddd72390d11102e7b4cb047b0f850c529a2101","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"南亞感謝日前夕 去咗重慶大廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁去重慶大廈就緊係周圍行吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食吓咖喱<br />\n同南亞手足吹下水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地都知聽日係懲罰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話依個星期多咗好多華人幫襯<br />\n咁一於聽日就罰到佢地收錢收到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結係<br />\n1）文宣要做足，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實好多商家都識廣東話，但識聽識講，唔識睇唔識寫<br />\n所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地唔太跟到依家主流嘅廣東話文宣，唔知社會近況係點，例如區議會選舉有咩人值得被選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）要多啲交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有啲南亞裔都好想同我地傾計，但好可惜廣東話唔得，聽日去嘅手足如果時間夠又好想搵南亞手足吹吓水都可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係地面雜貨店嘅南亞員工，佢地都好想知香港情況係點<br />\n<br />\n3）要注意禮貌<br />\n南亞其實好大，包括孟加拉印度巴基斯坦緬甸，有啲國家世仇嚟，例如印度vs 巴基斯坦，佢地因為宗教、領土問題都打咗好多次仗，所以同南亞人傾計，有啲人會估南亞人來自邊度，如果對方係印度人但你又話估佢係巴基斯坦人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就好似去外國人地估我地係大陸人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以都係等佢地自己講自己來自邊度好啲<br />\n另外重慶大廈都會有難民，佢地好避忌有人影佢地相，所以如果想打卡就避免影到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）南亞感謝日係要長期性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南亞手足佢地對自己係香港人嘅身份認同好強烈，但偏偏政府俾嘅融合資源唔夠，未有今個星期日嘅大遊行之前，我地仲係對南亞人有偏見，覺得重慶大廈係禁地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢並唔係最用嘅嘢，而係我地可以幫助到佢地融入我地嘅社會，真真正正令佢地覺得自己係香港人<br />\n<br />\nwe connect唔係齋講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係要show出嚟<br />\n佢地面對緊依啲障礙<br />\n<br />\n<ins>語言障礙</ins><br />\n好多時南亞手足講廣東話唔係好正，中文對佢地嚟講好困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過咗南亞感謝日會唔會有多啲義工教佢地嘅小朋友中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>被選權障礙</ins><br />\n<em>蘋果日報2012年嘅報道《植根港百年　巴漢被拒入籍　入境處原因：沒有近親是中國人》</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121213/18099692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121213%2F18099692&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=d08a2f64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20121213%2F18099692&h=37bdad73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20121213/18099692</a><br />\n裡面嗰位巴基斯坦手足簡浩名係深黃，雨傘革命就有去佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且水炮車射中清真寺佢都有致力幫我地發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攻勢同Mohan差唔多<br />\n同樣都係鬼佬嘅盛智文居然係有香港護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a11664a681d9b8c4aff2eb1a3af8a339efb27e2","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a89f64b61b04ac233b71f0ec046511ed0682fbd4","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"我要見到ust 南亞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317b37f4e5771d2054e5465e87e66c02fbe7db07","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2e1d367dd0ce0fe05c685f859107bcfca799588","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3c047371f87a358894ced328c2ae52520238e56","tid":1673392,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Squwor1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSquwor1.gif&h=dc4a280e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=778e77c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a877d18058ae73ef4e9c81af326934d5f3c550de","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"959551dcc43302ee0fa4b22391b55ebad731e7f6","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b14c15ff4df955f1534986c59d0706e7168bc84b","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6d3f493ab28a4f620f0d51e6c47882b615b7603","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:36:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa962d0192d3ca9273e6aaeb64167a33f75bdfd","tid":1673392,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ce1cf58b5ab4c7d7a9947100648e5a2d8334fc5","tid":1673392,"uid":225531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f29299f10d8a50f3573a01e07de1e552ae220e27","tid":1673392,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"396595a10e4255f23f47ad091d15a8da77609a5